{"tid":1573401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ C.朗落淚深感遺憾：父親未能見證我的成功","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T13:28:39.000Z","uid":25345,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ca02666ef65f649795187e467865b750e7ab599d","tid":1573401,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ronaldo.png?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;zoom=1&amp;resize=644%2C362&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fmetro.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fronaldo.png%3Fquality%3D90%26strip%3Dall%26zoom%3D1%26resize%3D644%252C362%26ssl%3D1&h=edbe1720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/09/16/1/116cafa9b2834c24cd89853b6377d350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2F1%2F116cafa9b2834c24cd89853b6377d350.jpg&h=69a87d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度近日作客知名主持人皮爾斯-摩根的節目，採訪期間，節目組放出了一組C.朗拿度父親生前的影像，C.朗拿度淚灑當場。C.朗拿度的父親在52歲時因酗酒導致肝功能衰竭而逝世，C.朗拿度表示很遺憾父親未能見證自己成功的每一步。<br />\n  C.朗拿度說：「我從未看過這個視頻，很不可思議。我原本以為採訪會很搞笑，但是我沒有料到我會哭。我從未看過這些影像。我不知道你們是從哪裡弄到的，我必須把這些影像給我的家人看。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我真的不算百分百瞭解我的父親，他是個酒鬼。我從來沒有和他有過一次像平常那樣的正常對話，這是很難的。」<br />\n  C.朗拿度的父親去世時，C.朗拿度只有20歲，因此父親沒能見證自己的成功，C.朗拿度對此很遺憾，他說：「我的家人看到了我的成功，我的媽媽，我的兄弟，甚至是我的大兒子，但是我的父親他什麼也沒看到，他很年輕就去世了。」"},{"pid":"2aebc42a5f9270b02a6147f46d59e53140eb7dee","tid":1573401,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ronaldo.png?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;zoom=1&amp;resize=644%2C362&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fmetro.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fronaldo.png%3Fquality%3D90%26strip%3Dall%26zoom%3D1%26resize%3D644%252C362%26ssl%3D1&h=edbe1720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37b9e8f26bfbbe76beaa2b412e7070fe2fe538f0","tid":1573401,"uid":25345,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/09/16/cac799e834b44d909ea85738bb9fc62d.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2Fcac799e834b44d909ea85738bb9fc62d.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=d9080bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/09/16/96bf43886f1446b48b83a3617ed62cf4.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2019%2F09%2F16%2F96bf43886f1446b48b83a3617ed62cf4.png%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=c2839fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc86b6c897874ac18ee4150a6bc14bf90e8fe25","tid":1573401,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"美斯&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;牙朗"},{"pid":"a2075eead7b756cc3903ebd40e54d159c1e3588d","tid":1573401,"uid":87155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"無張睇到呀屌"},{"pid":"3e8076c6c93033fe199b3cb799249351c2e210ae","tid":1573401,"uid":223256,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔係死老豆<br />\n你點會咁勁?"},{"pid":"38c6c4aece2348010e2bded267b3ebe530f95dd9","tid":1573401,"uid":222907,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3e8076c6c93033fe199b3cb799249351c2e210ae","tid":1573401,"uid":223256,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔係死老豆<br />\n你點會咁勁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"你個腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779384fb1ccacb6550bfe65cab85fbf7b0747a02","tid":1573401,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16